{"id":2862,"date":"2024-03-13T09:49:15","date_gmt":"2024-03-13T02:49:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2862"},"modified":"2024-03-13T09:49:15","modified_gmt":"2024-03-13T02:49:15","slug":"3-dieu-ban-can-hieu-ro-truoc-khi-lua-chon-nganh-luat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/3-dieu-ban-can-hieu-ro-truoc-khi-lua-chon-nganh-luat\/","title":{"rendered":"3 \u0110I\u1ec0U B\u1ea0N C\u1ea6N HI\u1ec2U R\u00d5 TR\u01af\u1edaC KHI L\u1ef0A CH\u1eccN NG\u00c0NH LU\u1eacT"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch l\u1eadp lu\u1eadn, x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cLu\u1eadt s\u01b0\u201d trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ai n\u00f3i cho b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc Lu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111am m\u00ea<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt nh\u01b0: ba m\u1eb9 mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc lu\u1eadt; kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh g\u00ec ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecdc lu\u1eadt; nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ng\u00e0nh lu\u1eadt; h\u1ecdc lu\u1eadt thu nh\u1eadp cao\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111i n\u1eefa, mu\u1ed1n s\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 2 t\u1eeb \u201c\u0111am m\u00ea\u201d. Ph\u1ea3i y\u00eau ng\u00e0nh n\u00e0y, \u0111am m\u00ea h\u1ecdc lu\u1eadt th\u00ec b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t, ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u00ean kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh n\u00e0y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc; th\u1ebf n\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111am m\u00ea b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o b\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i ng\u00e0nh lu\u1eadt kh\u00e1 kh\u00f4 khan, c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111am m\u00ea s\u1ebd th\u1ed5i h\u1ed3n v\u00e0o t\u1eebng m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n cho ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20352\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_4608-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ecfi ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecfi r\u1eb1ng: \u201cH\u1ecdc Lu\u1eadt c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ecfi ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef kh\u00f4ng?\u201d V\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00f3, n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a gi\u1ecfi h\u00e3y trau d\u1ed3i, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ecfi th\u00ec h\u00e3y ph\u00e1t huy v\u00e0 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ea1n v\u00ec gi\u1ecfi ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a v\u1ea1n n\u0103ng m\u1edf ra t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ecfi ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea5y. Ngo\u00e0i lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm Lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n trong nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 \u00e1n mang y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c kinh t\u1ebf, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp kinh t\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c am hi\u1ec3u lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p kinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n trong nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p l\u00fd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m khi ra tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>C\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111i s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4 khan c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u lu\u1eadt trong c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 lu\u1eadt. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n n\u1ebfu su\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n, ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh,\u2026 v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng tr\u00ed nh\u1edb h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng h\u1ebft kh\u1ed1i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 l\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i, b\u1ed5 sung ban h\u00e0nh m\u1edbi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh n\u00e0y th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ngay t\u1eeb n\u0103m nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15496\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15496\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-15496\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/IMG_1491-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15496\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean Lu\u1eadt Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00d4 t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh di\u1ec5n \u00e1n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt c\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ecdc t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 h\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho sinh vi\u00ean m\u00e0 \u201cTr\u0103m hay kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng tay quen\u201d, ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chui v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o sinh vi\u00ean Lu\u1eadt v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o, chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao. Th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, phi\u00ean t\u00f2a gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u1edbi <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/giang-vien-nganh-luat-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-xin-the-nao\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4 \u0111ang tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i TDD th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/sinh-vien-luat-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-thuc-tap-nhan-thuc-tai-van-phong-luat-su-hoang-huy\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Lu\u1eadt<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho c\u00e1c \u201cLu\u1eadt s\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d, v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1p l\u00fd trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u0103m 2024, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh c\u00e1c su\u1ea5t h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb mi\u1ec5n 50-100% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed cho c\u00e1c t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt trong th\u1eddi gian theo h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u0103m 2024, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 Tuy\u1ec3n sinh ng\u00e0nh <\/span><b>Lu\u1eadt:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>M\u00e3 ng\u00e0nh<\/strong>: <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7380101<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong>: <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A00, A01, C00, D01<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c 1: X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT 2023:<\/span>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1, h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2 l\u1edbp 11 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ba m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n l\u1edbp 12 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c 2: X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 k\u1ef3 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c 3: X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c 4: X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00e0i thi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u00ed sinh c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 g\u1ed3m:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT (gi\u1ea5y CNTN t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi), h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao CMND\/CCCD, gi\u1ea5y khai sinh, c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u01b0u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1c (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<a href=\"http:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/#dangkyxettuyen\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-11278 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Untitled-1-300x100.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\" \/><\/a><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh &#8211; <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, <\/span><b>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Hotline: 0934.078.668 &#8211;\u00a0 024.33.861.601<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch 2: Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i: <\/span><b>Website:<\/b><a href=\"http:\/\/www.thanhdo.edu.vn\"> <b>thanhdo.edu.vn<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ho\u1eb7c <\/span><b>Fanpage:<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch l\u1eadp lu\u1eadn, x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cLu\u1eadt s\u01b0\u201d trong t\u01b0